            <h3>The shift to remote work</h3>
            <p>Remote work increases endpoints outside of an office location, with workers logging on from anywhere through various reliable and unreliable means. As such, having an MDM became a priority overnight for protecting the organization.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4" purpose="report-note">
            <img src="/images/icon-certificate-36x36@2x.png">
            <h3>An upcoming compliance audit or certification</h3>
            <p>Another reason was that they had an upcoming compliance audit or certification, and probably knew they wouldn’t pass it without better monitoring and visibility into their endpoints.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4 mb-0" purpose="report-note">
            <img src="/images/icon-enrolled-device-36x36@2x.png">
