          <h3>22% say their MDM took over a year to implement</h3>
          <p>The largest segment of respondents (22.2%) reported that it took over a year to deploy and implement their MDM. However, for 18.7%, it took four weeks or less. For 15.7%, it took one to three months, and for 13.1% it took three to six months. For 16.2% it took six to nine months, and for 14.1% it took nine to twelve months.</p>
