        <h3>Top deployment challenges</h3>
        <p>What were some of the challenges to deployment? Respondents encountered the following while implementing their new MDM solution (and chose all that applied):</p>
        <div purpose="subsection" class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4" purpose="report-note">
            <img src="/images/icon-arrows-36x36@2x.png">
            <h3>Too complicated to configure</h3>
            <p>The biggest challenge was that the solution was too complicated to configure and to understand — a failure right at the start.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4" purpose="report-note">
            <img src="/images/icon-confusing-document-36x36@2x.png">
            <h3>Confusing or limited documentation</h3>
            <p>Possibly related to the confusion in the first reason, respondents also discovered there was a lack of documentation to help them deploy the solution, or the documentation was confusing.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4 mb-0" purpose="report-note">
