          <p>For those looking for a more efficient MDM that can help them achieve their goals of endpoint protection — and from what we discovered above, that may be half of organizations out there who find that their current MDM is insufficient — they want a solution that’s cloud-based, has built-in security defaults, is open source, is easy to set up, and gives real-time visibility.</p>
